#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Modern applications often need to run specific tasks periodically.\n"
"In this guide, you learn how to schedule periodic tasks."
msgstr "现代应用程序通常需要定期执行特定任务。在本指南中，您将学习如何安排定期任务。"

